casebody.data:
Craig MOSS, Appellant
v.
PENNSYLVANIA BOARD OF PROBATION AND PAROLE, Appellee No. 25 MAP 2018 Supreme Court of Pennsylvania. Decided: March 26, 2019

ORDER

PER CURIAM

AND NOW , this 26 th day of March, 2019, the Order of the Commonwealth Court is AFFIRMED . The Pennsylvania Board of Probation and Parole's Motion to Dismiss for Mootness is DENIED .
